<li>Temple, Julian, with Chris Salewicz, "Commentary on <i>The Great Rock 'n' Roll Swindle</i>" (<i>The Great Rock 'n' Roll Swindle</i> DVD bonus feature), Shout! Factory, 2001. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0738931993" class="internal">ISBN 0738931993</a></li>
<li>Thompson, Dave, <i>Alternative Rock</i>, Hal Leonard, 2000. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0879306076" class="internal">ISBN 0879306076</a></li>
