<li>Wall, Mick, <i>W.A.R.: The Unauthorized Biography of William Axl Rose</i>, Macmillan, 2008. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0312377673" class="internal">ISBN 0312377673</a></li>
</ul>
