<li id="cite_note-MM07-199">^ <a href="#cite_ref-MM07_199-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-MM07_199-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFMcLaren.2C_Malcolm2007">McLaren, Malcolm (15 September 2007). <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2007/sep/15/greatinterviews2" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2007/sep/15/greatinterviews2" rel="nofollow">"Searching for a Way to Break the Rules"</a>. <i>Guardian</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2007/sep/15/greatinterviews2" class="external free" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2007/sep/15/greatinterviews2" rel="nofollow">http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2007/sep/15/greatinterviews2</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 23 March 2009</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Searching+for+a+Way+to+Break+the+Rules&amp;rft.atitle=Guardian&amp;rft.aulast=McLaren%2C+Malcolm&amp;rft.au=McLaren%2C+Malcolm&amp;rft.date=15+September+2007&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Ftheguardian%2F2007%2Fsep%2F15%2Fgreatinterviews2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Sex_Pistols"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
