<li><a href="/wiki/Gavin_Walsh" title="Gavin Walsh">Walsh, Gavin</a>, <i>God Save the Sex Pistols: A Collector's Guide to the Priests Of Punk</i>, Plexus, 2003. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0859653161" class="internal">ISBN 0859653161</a></li>
